00:00:12.831 --> 00:00:15.430
Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi!

00:00:23.565 --> 00:00:26.996
What are you making today?
Mal Kova

00:00:36.018 --> 00:00:38.117
Ingredients required to make Mal Kova

00:00:38.458 --> 00:00:46.243
Custard Milk, Khova/Kova (dried whole milk),
Maida Flour, Milk Powder, Milk, Sugar, Cashews, Oil

00:00:56.409 --> 00:01:01.567
Mix some Nestle milkmaid, khova,
maida flour, milk powder &amp; milk (1 cup each)

00:01:28.292 --> 00:01:34.064
Take a pan and heat enough oil for deep frying

00:01:43.651 --> 00:01:51.301
Pour a ladle full of the mixed batter
and deep fry them as small patties

00:02:01.139 --> 00:02:06.803
Take them out as they turn golden brown
and dip them in sugar syrup

00:02:38.555 --> 00:02:45.685
Take the sugar dipped Mal Kova
into a serving plate

